@Patient.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5095
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_AUTH_LOGIN

### List all patients
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List patients by protocol
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients?protocolId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List patients by site and status
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients?siteId=1&status=Active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get patient by id
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enroll a new patient (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager / Investigator)
POST {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 5,
  "protocolId": 1,
  "siteId": 1,
  "enrollmentDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "Screened"
}

### Update patient
PUT {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 5,
  "protocolId": 1,
  "siteId": 1,
  "status": "Enrolled",
  "enrollmentDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "withdrawalDate": null,
  "withdrawalReason": null
}

### Withdraw patient
POST {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "withdrawalDate": "2026-09-15T00:00:00Z",
  "withdrawalReason": "Patient request — personal reasons"
}

### Soft-delete patient (Admin only)
DELETE {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Visits ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all visits
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List visits by status
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits?status=Scheduled
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List visits in date range
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits?scheduledFrom=2026-06-01&scheduledTo=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List visits for a specific patient
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits/patient/1?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get visit by id
GET {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schedule a visit (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager / Investigator)
POST {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "visitType": "Baseline Assessment",
  "scheduledDate": "2026-06-15T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "Scheduled",
  "notes": "Initial baseline visit — fasting required"
}

### Update visit
PUT {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visitType": "Baseline Assessment",
  "scheduledDate": "2026-06-15T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "Completed",
  "actualDate": "2026-06-15T09:30:00Z",
  "notes": "Completed — all samples collected"
}

### Soft-delete visit (Admin only)
DELETE {{Patient.API_HostAddress}}/api/visits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
